name: kemiibru
short_description: Dr. Anita Kemi Ibru, a USA educated OB/GYN specialist, announces her position as medical professional at Ideal Eagle Hospital within Lagos, Africa. The necessity for medical experts is usually clear throughout places with widespread poverty and also poor nutrition rates, and Doctor Anita Kemi Dasilva Ibru is proud to formally announce her placement with Ideal Eagle Hospital within Lagos, Nigeria. As with her other endeavors and health care work, Doctor Ibru is working hard to help meet the requirements of one of the principal subsets of Nigeria's populace.
